<eesti>Keeleoskust v&auml;hemalt algtasemel n&otilde;utakse avalikelt teenistujatelt ning valitsusasutuste hallatavate riigiasutuste ja kohaliku omavalitsuse asutuste t&ouml;&ouml;tajatelt, samuti avalik-&otilde;iguslike juriidiliste isikute ja nende asutuste t&ouml;&ouml;tajatelt, kelle teenistuskohustused v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;&uuml;lesanded on konkreetset laadi, keelekasutuskorrad on rutiinsed ja kirjalik t&ouml;&ouml; piirdub t&uuml;&uuml;pdokumentidega. </eesti>
<inglise>Language proficiency at least at the basic level is required from public servants, employees of state agencies administered by government agencies and of local government agencies, and from employees of legal persons in public law and agencies thereof whose duties of service or employment are of specific nature involving routine instances of language use and whose written assignments involve only standard documents. </inglise>
