<inglise>Language proficiency at least at the intermediate level is required from public servants, employees of state agencies administered by government agencies and of local government agencies, and from employees of legal persons in public law and agencies thereof whose duties of service or employment are varied and may be related to records management, management of a subordinate unit and co-operation and the nature of whose written work can be defined. </inglise>
